Part of the graph of $f(x) = ax^3 + bx^2 + cx + d$ is shown. What is $b$?

[asy]
unitsize(1.5 cm);

real func(real x) {
  return((x + 1)*(x - 1)*(x - 2));
}

draw(graph(func,-1.1,1.5));
draw((-1.5,0)--(1.5,0),Arrows(6));
